document_data.Notable annis hags:
* [[Gremma]], a powerful annis hag who controlled a group of [[ogre]]s, and owned a magical cauldron.
* [[Tanta Hagara]], an annis who acted as a [[shaman]] and leader for the [[Blue Bear tribe]] in [[1358 DR]] who sought to find the ancestral mound beneath the [[Grandfather Tree]].
* [[Vexia]], an annis that was once part of a coven with a sea and green hag in [[Cormanthyr|Cormanthyr.]] She was eventually banished and cursed to resemble a [[nymph]].<ref>{{Cite dungeon/29/Nymph's Reward}}
